stateDiagram-v2
direction LR
Idle : Waiting for work
state "Processing Order" as Processing
state Decision <<choice>>
state Fork <<fork>>
state Join <<join>>
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Processing : begin
Processing --> Decision : validate
Decision --> Fork : accepted
Decision --> Idle : rejected
Fork --> Join : branch complete
Join --> [*] : done
note right of Processing : External service call
note left of Idle
  No pending jobs.
end note
